{"tid":929093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"低胸賣魚妹太正！網友揪團到彰化：買魚了","createTime":"2018-12-05T10:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T11:19:12.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"abd0af2272ba93bc95d8c8abf51f2544d92234b1","tid":929093,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"網友在《臉書》社團「爆廢公社二館」貼出賣魚正妹的照片，可見穿著細肩帶背心的正妹，在賣魚攤招呼客人買魚，全妝的她在市場中特別明顯，發文網友還笑說「媽，我以後都幫你去買魚。」<br />\n <br />\n照片一出立刻有網友討論，「好美的闆娘」、「突然想吃魚」，還有人說「媽以後我幫你去彰化社頭買魚會比較久一點」、「跪求賣魚西施FB」、「我社頭人，我要回外婆家了。」但也有眼尖網友認出，「應該只有我感覺沒有很熟練」、「這不是阿澎嗎？」、「麻豆也兼職賣魚嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CryCbZ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCryCbZ4.png&h=0af3218a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8bL5j5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8bL5j5.png&h=0ec8c18d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49m8iE6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49m8iE6.png&h=c4b46419&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d85510836156f6cfb61fbaf4e15d903b7607b0f3","tid":929093,"uid":20317,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"悶到，次次都用呢招，又唔係靚又唔係大波"},{"pid":"c8d9a6220ee7ce13479b2f03ecfa6f945470b9e6","tid":929093,"uid":24737,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"化行妝去賣魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a54e48cd666a3e5f978fcaae2922afaa3ffaad","tid":929093,"uid":120070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"我知佢邊個  佢咩都撈 鄉下巡遊啲跳舞"},{"pid":"adcd83c0a1dfba26ae20c80b98c96e4e47984a99","tid":929093,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"似泰國人妖"},{"pid":"bd3ad31233370e60049c693c5e612e6767da7ab3","tid":929093,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018